title: The Brookline cockatoo is back in its cage
text:
The Brookline cockatoo is back in its cage 
Published By: Boston.com - Today 
Dino, the cockatoo who escaped from his cage and has terrorized Brookline residents since July, was captured Thursday afternoon....
